net.metro.systemobjects

  • Packages that use net.metro.systemobjects 
    Package Description
    net.metro.analyze  
    net.metro.systemobjects  
  • Classes in net.metro.systemobjects used by net.metro.analyze 
    Class and Description
    Period
    Object that defines a time period within which a Service operates.
    Route
    Object that defines a Route and its paths and waypoints, as well as services and data.
    RoutePath
    Object that defines one path of a particular route using a series of WayPoints and Stops.
    Service
    Object that provides information about a particular path of a route during a specific time of day and time of the week.
    ServiceStop
    Object that stores data information regarding occurrences at a particular along a route path.
    Stop
    Object that defines a stop of a route on a particular route path.
    SystemObjects
    This is a container database of all objects relating to routes, route paths, stops, waypoints, services, and data.
    WayPoint
    Object describing a point visited by a route along its route path.
